                        <note n="3" xml:id="note-t-3">
                            

<p>This remark refers to the fact that Van Gogh had ingested paint during his attack. It was not the first time he had done this (<ref target="let794.xml#n-1">see letter 794, n. 1</ref>).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
